{"tid":857923,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"到底點解每次都係我地比左膠騎劫？點解我地唔可以騎劫左膠一次？","createTime":"2018-10-11T12:08:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T12:24:53.000Z","uid":11055,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3d1ce539b74564bb6c2af89d9f09a02d5981f555","tid":857923,"uid":11055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T12:08:56.000Z","msg":"雨革，你話比左膠騎，比熱狗篤，<br />\n所以失敗。<br />\n魚革，又話係春藥黃垃圾，所以最後比人清。<br />\n咁問心，到底咩人最有號召力叫最多人出黎？<br />\n係啊，係左膠，因為和平入血入骨既港豬，<br />\n係唔會因為我地呢一代提倡既「獨」而站出黎！<br />\n咁點解我地可以比左膠劫咁多次，<br />\n唔可以組織一次行動，係佢地號召既行動入面，<br />\n反劫返佢地一次？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5270973bdf886686eb4a81df851e45236dc41dcd","tid":857923,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T12:23:02.000Z","msg":"騎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c75a76dfd281a9ceca806e50c81d11a6ae90722","tid":857923,"uid":38041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T12:24:53.000Z","msg":"因為左膠嘅精神係港人核心價值 <br />\n每日都喺擠迫嘅狗鐵站顯現出嚟"}]}